{"tid":2395803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國安法」同美國獨立戰爭前夕英國做嘅嘢一模一樣","createTime":"2021-02-05T06:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T08:42:36.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc76a264900bf3c491f108192cb61ba8a086f9f4","tid":2395803,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953813238188081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2953813238188081&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=7bdfad8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953813238188081</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2218174475085298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2218174475085298&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=edc116b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2218174475085298</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n「國安法」同美國比唔係乜春國家安全法律，係美國獨立前夕嘅1766年宣示法令 Declaratory Act, 1766。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953816684854403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2953816684854403&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=1d7e6c75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953816684854403</a><br />\n<br />\n美國獨立戰爭前夕，英國國會撒回一系列稅項法令， 然後直接立一份在北美直接生效嘅法令「宣示」自己嘅主權。同香港撤回逃犯條例然後做嘅嘢唔係一模一樣咩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953818634854208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2953818634854208&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=b34aae07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953818634854208</a><br />\n<br />\n普通法傳統應該被神化係因為源頭嘅帝國乜都經歷過曬，壞人呃你係新鮮嘅嘢，往往係英美法律史搵到，明未？"},{"pid":"ac9d8b9daacfa0c522b70a942d5dae3dc15787fa","tid":2395803,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"Jm9"},{"pid":"b82199719099d6965cfe328a352b170ce07190e3","tid":2395803,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc76a264900bf3c491f108192cb61ba8a086f9f4","tid":2395803,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953813238188081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2953813238188081&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=7bdfad8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953813238188081</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2218174475085298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2218174475085298&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=edc116b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2218174475085298</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n「國安法」同美國比唔係乜春國家安全法律，係美國獨立前夕嘅1766年宣示法令 Declaratory Act, 1766。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953816684854403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2953816684854403&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=1d7e6c75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953816684854403</a><br />\n<br />\n美國獨立戰爭前夕，英國國會撒回一系列稅項法令， 然後直接立一份在北美直接生效嘅法令「宣示」自己嘅主權。同香港撤回逃犯條例然後做嘅嘢唔係一模一樣咩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2953818634854208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2953818634854208&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=b34aae07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts